---
import SectionLabel from "../../elements/SectionLabel.astro";
---

<section class="py-32 px-6 md:px-10">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[900px]">
    <SectionLabel
      text="> SYS.PREP // MISSION_BRIEF"
      class="text-rh-chalk/50! mb-12"
    />

    <h2
      class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-normal leading-[1.1] text-rh-chalk mb-12"
    >
      Prepare for<br />Your Session.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div
        class="flex gap-6 p-6 rounded-xl border border-rh-chalk/10 bg-rh-warm-dark"
      >
        <div
          class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-rh-ember flex items-center justify-center font-heading font-black text-lg text-white"
        >
          1
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3
            class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-rh-chalk mb-2 uppercase"
          >
            Fill Out the Intake Form Below
          </h3>
          <p class="text-rh-chalk/70 leading-relaxed">
            This helps us understand your current ecosystem, goals, and
            challenges before we meet. The more context you share, the more
            value we can deliver in our session.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div
        class="flex gap-6 p-6 rounded-xl border border-rh-chalk/10 bg-rh-warm-dark"
      >
        <div
          class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-rh-ember flex items-center justify-center font-heading font-black text-lg text-white"
        >
          2
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3
            class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-rh-chalk mb-2 uppercase"
          >
            Check Your Email
          </h3>
          <p class="text-rh-chalk/70 leading-relaxed">
            You'll receive a calendar invite with the meeting link and session
            details. Add it to your calendar so nothing slips through the
            cracks.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div
        class="flex gap-6 p-6 rounded-xl border border-rh-chalk/10 bg-rh-warm-dark"
      >
        <div
          class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-rh-ember flex items-center justify-center font-heading font-black text-lg text-white"
        >
          3
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3
            class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-rh-chalk mb-2 uppercase"
          >
            Think About Your Community Vision
          </h3>
          <p class="text-rh-chalk/70 leading-relaxed">
            Where are you today? Where do you want to be in 6 months? What's
            the biggest bottleneck? Come ready to think big. We'll handle the
            architecture.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
